"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1126948","Ministry of Defence","false","2019-05-21","<p>Since 2015 UK Naval ships have visited the Baltic states as part of Standing NATO Maritime Group 1 for six visits and as part of Standing NATO Mine Countermeasures Group 1 for 15 visits.</p>","Milton Keynes North","Mark Lancaster",,"2019-05-21T14:59:31.52Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1126948/answer","Biography information for Mark Lancaster","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1126948/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1126948/answer",,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2019-05-15","Baltic States: Navy","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, how many times UK ships have visited the Baltic states as part of Standing NATO Maritime Group One since 2015.","false","Biography information for Andrew Rosindell","Romford","Andrew Rosindell","254771"
